evaṃ kathitanayena. sādhūktam iti cet, adhunā vada kasmāt tvam adyāpi sarvaguṇavikalam api kāyaṃ rakṣasi? evaṃ vidvān api.

<commentary>tathāpi asti kiṃcidatropādeyamiti cedāha-

na khāditavyamaśuci tvayā peyaṃ na śoṇitam |
nāntrāṇi cūṣitavyāni kiṃ kāyena kariṣyasi || Bca_5.65 ||

yadasti, na tadupayuktamiti saṃkṣepārthaḥ | ataḥ kimanupayoginā kāyena kariṣyasi? atra āsaṅgo na yukta ityarthaḥ ||</commentary>

anyaprayojanābhāvād idam evocitam utpaśyāmaḥ ity āha. yasmāt karmaṇi kenacit sahakāribhāvenopayujyate iti rakṣyate.